item.title: Netherlands - A Day Trip to Den Haag 20240728
item.description: This trip was all about heading to the beach, so we didn’t visit many places. I originally planned to go next week, but suddenly noticed that the weather was fantastic this weekend, with temperatures around 30°C. The weather in the Netherlands changes quickly, and good weather doesn’t last long, so I decided to seize the day and head out. I won’t go into details about transportation, as I’m staying in the Netherlands for six months and have already bought an OV card with a weekend free plan.
